# Feature Architecture

- Keep feature code self-contained under `src/app/features/<feature>/`.
- Standard layout: `pages/`, `components/`, `services/`, `<feature>.routes.ts`, `index.ts`.
- Feature components/services must not depend directly on other feature internals.
- Cross-feature reuse goes through shared APIs (`index.ts`) or `src/app/shared/`.
- Put truly global concerns in `src/app/core/`, not in feature folders.

## Placement Rules

- Shared reusable UI belongs in `src/app/shared/ui/`.
- Feature-specific logic belongs in the feature `services/` folder.
